{"id":"441c91f2-6ddb-4161-9ed4-dc15b80dceb1","name":"Satoru Gojo","description":"<p><strong>My Annoying, Master</strong> | \"You made me all dirty, User.\"</p><p>You are his personal maid.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"\" alt=\"Displayed GIF\" src=\"https://i.postimg.cc/Dzj9CHpG/GIF-20250224-151549-926.gif\"></p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Satoru + boredom in Kyoto = pure chaos.</p><p></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Luckily, there’s the new maid, User, whom he immediately declares his personal plaything. Golden spoons, ridiculous movie nights, and outrageously bold demands, he loves driving her crazy.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_ef1a732d-40a2-4ea7-8b6f-2abd9ae8b04d.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>I love it when he's a spoiled, sweet baby. He deserves a little love.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><strong>Quick question: Do you prefer the story images I usually use, or do you like the short video format better?</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/91ef5ed3-43c1-49d3-aa6b-3916c5f82455_9b712fd9-8c75-412d-9db8-519ce63d8f8e.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(44, 217, 217)\"><strong>More Pictures and Infos</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/7sAqFCQyWOyqp8W4QckLn.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"ht